{
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "reason": "恢复正常状态"
}

### 13.2.8 调整用户信用等级
PATCH {{baseUrl}}:{{userServicePort}}/admin/users/1/credit
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "creditLevel": 5
}

### 13.2.9 获取用户活动日志
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{userServicePort}}/admin/users/1/activity
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==================== 13.3 商家管理 API ====================

### 13.3.1 获取商家统计数据
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{merchantServicePort}}/api/admin/merchants/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.3.2 获取活跃商家数
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{merchantServicePort}}/api/admin/merchants/active-count
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.3.3 获取最新注册商家
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{merchantServicePort}}/api/admin/merchants/latest?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.3.4 获取商家列表（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{merchantServicePort}}/api/admin/merchants?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.3.5 获取商家详情
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{merchantServicePort}}/api/admin/merchants/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.3.6 修改商家状态
PATCH {{baseUrl}}:{{merchantServicePort}}/api/admin/merchants/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 13.3.7 审批商家
PATCH {{baseUrl}}:{{merchantServicePort}}/api/admin/merchants/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true,
  "reason": "资质审核通过"
}

### ==================== 13.4 订单管理 API ====================

### 13.4.1 获取订单统计数据
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{orderServicePort}}/api/admin/orders/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.4.2 获取总销售额
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{orderServicePort}}/api/admin/orders/total-sales
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.4.3 获取今日订单数
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{orderServicePort}}/api/admin/orders/today-count
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.4.4 获取订单趋势（最近7天）
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{orderServicePort}}/api/admin/orders/trends
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.4.5 获取所有订单（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{orderServicePort}}/api/admin/orders/all?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.4.6 按状态筛选订单
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{orderServicePort}}/api/admin/orders/all?page=0&size=10&status=COMPLETED
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.4.7 获取订单详情
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{orderServicePort}}/api/admin/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13.4.8 修改订单状态
PATCH {{baseUrl}}:{{orderServicePort}}/api/admin/orders/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

